    "mc_th_text_slide_7Eziwp": {
      "type": "mc_th-text-slide",
      "blocks": {
        "slide_Qk3WYw": {
          "type": "slide",
          "settings": {
            "subtitle": "June 5 – June 8",
            "title": "Free Order Chance",
            "intro": "1st Anniversary Celebration",
            "pc_image": "shopify://shop_images/th-slide-image1.jpg",
            "subhead": "<p>Top Customer Wins!</p>",
            "subhead_decorate_image": "shopify://shop_images/th-text-bottom-image1.png",
            "decorate_image_height": 27,
            "subhead_color": "#ffffff",
            "head": "<p>Free Order Chance</p>",
            "head_color": "#ffffff",
            "show_button": true,
            "button_text": "Learn more >",
            "button_url": "",
            "button_color": "#ffffff",
            "button_bg_color": "#d30000",
            "slide_desc": "<p>Q1: How does the Free Order event work?<br/>A1: From June 5 – June 8, the first customer each day to successfully place an eligible order will win a Free Order reward. After the event ends, winners will be contacted via email.<br/><br/>Q2: How is the “first order of the day” determined?<br/>A2: The winner will be determined based on the official order timestamp recorded by our system. Orders must be successfully placed and paid during the event period.<br/><br/>Q3: When and how will winners be notified?<br/>A3: All winners will be notified via email after the event ends. Please make sure the email address used at checkout is valid and check your inbox (including spam/junk folders).<br/><br/>Q4: How will I receive my refund if I win?<br/>A4: If selected as a winner, your order amount will be fully refunded to your original payment method after your order is completed and verified. Refund processing time may vary depending on your payment provider.<br/><br/>Q5: Are there any restrictions or conditions?<br/>A5: Only completed and eligible orders qualify. Cancelled orders, refunded orders, duplicate entries, or suspicious activity may be disqualified. Yozma reserves the right to verify eligibility and make the final decision regarding the event.</p>"
          }
        },
        "slide_aKxrF9": {
          "type": "slide",
          "settings": {
            "subtitle": "June 9 – June 10",
            "title": "Win Insta360 Camera",
            "intro": "Capture your ride moments",
            "pc_image": "shopify://shop_images/th-slide-image4.jpg",
            "subhead": "<p>Double the Fun! </p>",
            "subhead_decorate_image": "shopify://shop_images/th-text-bottom-image2.png",
            "decorate_image_height": 18,
            "subhead_color": "#ffffff",
            "head": "<p>Win Insta360  Camera </p>",
            "head_color": "#ffffff",
            "show_button": true,
            "button_text": "Learn more >",
            "button_url": "",
            "button_color": "#ffffff",
            "button_bg_color": "#d30000",
            "slide_desc": "<p>Q1: How does the Free Insta360 event work?<br/>A1: The event runs from June 9 – June 10. The first successfully paid order each day that includes a complete bike purchase will win a free Insta360 camera. A total of 2 winners will be selected.<br/><br/>Q2: Which Insta360 model will I receive? Can I choose the model?<br/>A2: The free gift model is Insta360 GO 3S. The model, version, and color cannot be selected or changed.<br/><br/>Q3: How and when will winners be announced?<br/>A3: Winners will be contacted via email after the event ends. Please make sure the email used at checkout is valid and check your spam/junk folder if needed.<br/><br/>Q4: When will the free Insta360 be shipped?<br/>A4: The free Insta360 gift will be arranged after the order has been completed and verified. Shipping timing may vary depending on processing status.<br/><br/>Q5: Does the free Insta360 include warranty or after-sales service?<br/>A5: The free gift does not include after-sales service or warranty support. Yozma reserves the right of final verification and interpretation of the event rules.</p>"
          }
        },
