            "slide_desc": "<p>Q1: What is the “Signed Belgium Player Merch” and is the signature authentic?<br/>A1: The Signed Belgium Player Merch is a limited-edition promotional reward signed by a Belgium national team player. All signatures are authentic and provided as part of the official campaign collaboration.\"<br/><br/>Q2: How do I get  the Signed Belgium Player Merch?<br/>A2: During the campaign( 6.16 – 6.18), the customer with the highest order value will win the signed merch. If multiple orders have the same value, the earliest completed order will be selected.\"<br/><br/>Q3: When will I receive the signed item?<br/>A3: The signed item is available in very limited quantities and be shipped separately after the main order has been successfully delivered and completed (no return or refund).\"<br/><br/>Q4: Can I choose which player’s signature I receive or exchange, return, or redeem the signed merch?<br/>A4: No. All signed items are randomly assigned, and specific players cannot be selected. Signed merch is a limited promotional reward and is non-exchangeable, non-returnable, and not redeemable for cash or other products.\"<br/><br/>Q5: Will I still keep the Signed Belgium Player Merch reward if I cancel or return my order?<br/>A5: No. If the order is canceled, refunded, or returned, the reward eligibility will be removed. The signed merch will only be awarded after the original order has been successfully delivered and completed.\"</p>"
          }
        },
        "slide_6BeDbt": {
          "type": "slide",
          "settings": {
            "subtitle": "June 19 – June 30",
            "title": "Free Cycling Safety Set",
            "intro": "Create unforgettable moments together",
            "pc_image": "shopify://shop_images/th-slide-image3.jpg",
