            "show_button": true,
            "button_text": "Learn more >",
            "button_url": "",
            "button_color": "#ffffff",
            "button_bg_color": "#d30000",
            "slide_desc": "<p>Q1: When does the Family Riding Event start and end?<br/>A2: The Family Riding Event runs from June 19 to June 30. All event rewards and offers are only available during this limited-time period.\"<br/><br/>Q2: How does the extra $150 OFF promotion work?<br/>A2: Customers who purchase two bikes in a single order will automatically receive an extra $150 OFF at checkout. No code is needed.\"<br/><br/>Q3: Will I receive a free riding bag with my order?<br/>A4: Yes. Customers who place an eligible order during the event will receive a free riding bag while supplies last.\"<br/><br/>Q4: Can I combine the Family Riding Event promotions with other offers?<br/>A5: Some promotions may be combined, while certain rewards or limited-time offers may have separate terms and conditions. Please check the official event page for full details before ordering.<br/><br/>Q5: What prizes are included in the lucky wheel event?<br/>A5: Participants may have a chance to win rewards such as $200 OFF, $100 OFF, $50 OFF, a free bike opportunity, a free-order opportunity, an IN 10 battery, keychains, and other surprise prizes.\"</p>"
          }
