    "faq_HNmJpq": {
      "type": "faq",
      "blocks": {
        "item_3Up9xE": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "title": "1. When does the campaign take place?",
            "content": "<p>The campaign is divided into three phases:</p><ul><li>Anniversary Rush: June 5 – June 10<br/></li><li>Belgium Team Collaboration: June 16 – June 18<br/></li><li>Family Ride Event: June 19 – June 30<br/></li></ul>"
          }
        },
        "item_rhGzFK": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "title": "2. How do I join the Lucky Wheel, and what can I win?",
            "content": "<p>Enter the campaign page and submit your email to participate.<br/><br/>After registration, you will be automatically subscribed to our updates and receive 1 spin.</p><p><strong>Lucky Wheel rewards include:</strong></p><ul><li>$200 / $100 / $50 / $20 discount coupons<br/></li><li>Free bike (IN 10 Red)<br/></li><li>Free order (refund opportunity)<br/></li><li>IN 10 battery<br/></li><li>Helmet, keychain, and riding accessories<br/></li></ul><p>All rewards are non-cashable and can only be used in-store.</p>"
          }
        },
        "item_g6ycrU": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "title": "3. Are there any additional gifts or bonuses?",
            "content": "<p>(Applicable to: June 5 – June 10 / June 16 – June 18)</p><p>Eligible orders during the campaign will receive limited-time perks:</p><ul><li>Anniversary Gift Box (limited, while supplies last)<br/></li><li>1-Year Extended Warranty<br/></li></ul><p><strong>Additional offers by period:</strong></p><ul><li>June 19 – June 30: Extra $150 OFF when purchasing 2 bikes (auto-applied discount)<br/></li></ul><p>Gift box includes branded items such as T-shirt, cap, stickers, wristband, and keychain, and may ship separately from the bike, with no after-sales service for gifts.<br/><br/></p>"
          }
        },
        "item_gae7Mm": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "title": "4. Are there any special reward events?",
            "content": "<p>Different phases include special surprises:</p><ul><li>June 5 – June 8: Daily first full-bike order  receive a free order reward</li><li>June 9 – June 10: Daily first full-bike order may receive an Insta360 camera 📷</li><li>June 16 – June 18: Limited signed jersey giveaway (only 1 available), awarded to the customer with the highest order value, or in the case of a tie, the earliest payment wins.<br/></li><li>June 19 – June 30: Get an additional $150 off when you purchase two units.</li></ul>"
          }
        },
        "item_ygGRLP": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "title": "5. How does the “Top Order” reward work?",
            "content": "<p>(Applicable to: June 5 – June 8)</p><p>Orders are ranked by payment time:</p><ul><li>1st place: Free bike (full refund)<br/></li><li>2nd–10th: Riding gear set (helmet + gloves + bike bag)<br/></li><li>11th–20th: Goggles</li></ul>"
          }
        },
        "item_7hjpax": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "title": "6. What discounts are available in the Belgium Team Collaboration campaign?",
            "content": "<p>(Applicable to: June 16 – June 18)</p><ul><li>$1499 → $100 OFF<br/></li><li>$2199 → $200 OFF<br/></li><li>$2999 → $300 OFF<br/></li></ul>"
          }
        },
        "item_mUqj43": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "title": "7. How will winners be notified?",
            "content": "<p>All winners will be notified via email after each campaign period ends.</p>"
          }
        },
        "item_YTYbjJ": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "title": "8. Can rewards be transferred or exchanged for cash?",
            "content": "<p>No. All rewards are non-transferable and cannot be exchanged for cash. They are valid only for the original order.</p>"
          }
        },
        "item_8Rp9qE": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "title": "9. What happens if I return my order?",
            "content": "<p>If an order is returned or refunded, all related rewards and gifts will be invalid and may need to be returned if already received.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
